DO NOT EDIT these files. To update, re-fetch the two files from the upstream
tag, e.g.:
  curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LoupVaillant/Monocypher/<TAG>/src/monocypher.c -o lib/monocypher/src/monocypher.c
  curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LoupVaillant/Monocypher/<TAG>/src/monocypher.h -o lib/monocypher/src/monocypher.h

Used by MeshRoute (lib/core/identity) for the node Ed25519/X25519 identity keypair.
Note: monocypher's crypto_eddsa_* is curve25519+BLAKE2b (NOT RFC-8032 SHA-512). For
RFC-8032 interop, vendor src/optional/monocypher-ed25519.{c,h} as well.
